                                 Solution

Each Scene is defined as where you resume if you die!

Scene 1: Press UP when the wizard fires at you.  During your jump press
FIRE.  Press FIRE while running.  When you appear at the top of the cliff,
press RIGHT.

Scene 2: Press FIRE Immediately.

Scene 3: When shield appears around you, press FIRE.

Scene 4: Wait thru pause, when TweedleDee puts hat on you, press LEFT.

Scene 5: Press LEFT immediately.

Scene 6: Immediately press UP.  When you land, press DOWN.  After pause,
right before queen's scream, press FIRE.

Scene 7: Press RIGHT immediately.

Scene 8: Immediately press FIRE.  When screen changes, press to the LEFT.
After getting on horse, press FIRE when screen changes.

Scene 9: Immediately press UP.  While in the air, press LEFT.  Press RIGHT
when screen changes.

Scene 10: While the dragon puffs up, press FIRE.  When screen changes,
immediately press LEFT.  When you land on the ground, press UP.  When the
screen changes, press RIGHT.

Scene 11: While riding on dragon's head, press LEFT.  When shield appears,
press FIRE.

Scene 12: When music stops, press UP.

Scene 13: When you land, press LEFT.  While in the air, press DOWN.  When
you land next to mug, press RIGHT.  While running of edge of screen press
RIGHT.  After leap, press DOWN.  On your way to the ground, press FIRE.
While swinging your sword, press UP.

Scene 14: Immediately press LEFT.  When you land on cup, press DOWN.

Scene 15: When you see cat's paw, press RIGHT.  Immediately followed by
pressing FIRE.

Scene 16: While in the air, press FIRE.  When you are running on the
ground, press FIRE.

Scene 17: When your teleporter appears, press LEFT.

Scene 18: When captain yells, press FIRE.  While falling into barrel,
press DOWN.  Immediately followed by pressing RIGHT.

Scene 19: Before you get to the end of the plank, press RIGHT.  When you
start to fall, press UP.  When you land on ropes, press FIRE.  While you
slice the pirate, press UP.  When you land on top of the ship, press FIRE.

Scene 20: When you land, press FIRE.  During your slice, press FIRE.

Scene 21: When you land on path, press DOWN.  While the clock jumps over
you, press FIRE.  When screen changes, press FIRE.  As you enter the
palace, press LEFT.

Scene 22: While running towards clock, press UP.  When you reach top of
clock, immediately press UP.  Once inside clock, immediately press RIGHT.
While in the air, press UP.  As you approach the door, press RIGHT.

Scene 23: After you smash through the clock, wait for screen to change and
press RIGHT.  While in the air, press UP.  As soon as screen changes,
immediately press RIGHT.  Immediately press RIGHT.

Scene 24: Wait for screen to change, press DOWN.  While picking up the
mirror, press LEFT.

Scene 25: Immediately press DOWN.  While in the air, press RIGHT.  Before
landing, press RIGHT.  Before you land on your teleporter, press FIRE.

Congratulations, YOU WIN!

