Never ever attempt to go into the sewers without the torch.

To get lots of points do any of the following: Go to the Pizza Party (a
building without a sign on it).  Waggle your joystick left and right to
eat pizzas.  When you get splatted by a pie you'll fall down a hole to the
sewers.  If you've eaten a lot you'll see a pizza monster!

and) Take the golf ball from the shed to the golf course (the scene before
the busty lady picture).  Kick it to try for a hole in one.  If you miss
you'll find the ball near the busty lady.

and) Jump on the settee and kick it.  You'll then see that it's ripped.

